      "content": "i mean i get the moral part, but you're calling the other side a \"false narrative\" and saying their arguments are \"outdated.\" isn't that a bit much? isn't it possible that there are valid economic reasons to prefer a private system, or are you saying those viewpoints are just wrong?",
